INSERT INTO
                lobbies (game_id, teams, max_players, game_map, approx_num_players, first_seen_unix_sec, last_seen_unix_sec)
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (game_id)
            DO UPDATE
                SET approx_num_players = $5
                , last_seen_unix_sec = $6
